    <briefdescription>
<para>Delay state. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Dual-buffer circular delay line. The backing store is a contiguous allocation of 2*capacity elements: the first half is the live ring; the second half mirrors it so that any window of num_taps consecutive samples is always contiguous in memory (no wrap-around copy needed).</para>
<para>Allocate with <ref refid="delay__core_8h_1a4c8caf168aa7819d3c39a7af2d38dfad" kindref="member">delay_create()</ref>. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
